schools.name: St. Lucie West Centennial High School

data.description: Seller wants this sold! Bring all offers, under market price! Heritage Oaks 3 bedroom , 2 bath , featuring eat in kitchen, formal dining area. Perfect layout with high ceilings. Needs some TLC,  paint and carpet. Beautiful greenery in front and back. New Lennox Air Condition just installed with 10 year Warranty . Community has a great pool area, club house and gym plus a guard gated entrance. Traditions has great shopping and dining plus lots of festivals and activities. Last but not least so convenient to I-95 and the Florida Turnpike.
